metadata.name: Porcelain People
metadata.description:
The Porcelain people arrived via ML algorithms as mysterious digital blemishes from right across the digital Renaissance. Almost Life drawings prompts from the dataset ether. They inhabit their own world now. 

AI + Digital painting. 4000px x 4000px.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
